Oh, God!

477
00:52:19,755 --> 00:52:22,424
General, are you all right?

478
00:52:22,508 --> 00:52:24,593
Yeah.

479
00:52:56,875 --> 00:53:01,421
OK, you guys. Come on.
Gather your stuff and move!

480
00:53:12,224 --> 00:53:14,726
- This is it, Jim.
- OK, sir.

481
00:53:19,273 --> 00:53:20,858
You OK?

482
00:53:20,941 --> 00:53:22,860
Right. Let's go.

483
00:53:25,988 --> 00:53:28,157
Then keep trying.

484
00:53:28,240 --> 00:53:30,492
There must be someone there!

485
00:53:33,036 --> 00:53:36,123
My apologies.
I can get no sense from anybody.

486
00:53:36,248 --> 00:53:38,792
They say thousands of troops
are dropping over Holland.

487
