I can't get through to his headquarters.

489
00:53:45,632 --> 00:53:48,719
A strong force has landed
south of Nijmegen.

490
00:53:48,844 --> 00:53:52,055
Nijmegen? They're after the bridge.

491
00:53:54,766 --> 00:53:58,520
