Now listen.

494
00:54:06,111 --> 00:54:08,238
I¡¯ll take care of Arnhem.

495
00:54:08,322 --> 00:54:11,742
You get to Nijmegen as fast as you can.

496
00:54:11,867 --> 00:54:13,202
Take anything that'll move...

497
