So no one's going to get to
Arnhem Bridge except on foot. Splendid.

511
00:55:47,129 --> 00:55:52,342
They must be from the lunatic asylum, sir.
It's located on the far side of the wood.

512
00:55:52,426 --> 00:55:56,430
They escaped
when it was bombed this morning.

513
00:56:00,934 --> 00:56:04,897
Do you think
they know something we don't?

514
00:56:18,285 --> 00:56:20,662
All guns commence firing!

515
00:56:33,383 --> 00:56:35,427
Get moving.

516
00:56:35,511 --> 00:56:38,013
Driver advance.

517
00:58:40,761 --> 00:58:43,931
Message received. Thank you. Out.

518
00:59:50,956 --> 00:59:53,041
Start the purple!

519
00:59:53,709 --> 00:59:56,128
Start the purple!

520
