to blow up the bridges
at Arnhem and Nijmegen.

554
01:05:35,759 --> 01:05:37,511
That is out of the question.

555
01:05:37,594 --> 01:05:40,013
Never. Is that clear?

556
01:05:40,097 --> 01:05:42,015
We need them for our counterattack.

557
01:05:42,099 --> 01:05:44,810
Counterattack? With what?

558
01:05:44,893 --> 01:05:47,855
Paratroopers cannot fight long.
They are too lightly equipped.

559
01:05:47,938 --> 01:05:50,023
Isolated they are lost.

560
01:05:50,149 --> 01:05:52,734
I have spoken to Von Rundstedt.

561
01:05:52,860 --> 01:05:56,363
All reinforcements come to us first.

562
01:05:56,446 --> 01:05:59,616
Every hour we get stronger
and they grow weaker.

563
01:05:59,741 --> 01:06:04,246
- But if we blow the bridges...
- They don't want the bridges.

564
01:06:04,371 --> 01:06:06,498
Do you really think
if they wanted the bridges...

565
01:06:06,582 --> 01:06:10,544
