12 kilometres away?

566
01:06:10,669 --> 01:06:12,546
It's ridiculous.

567
01:06:16,800 --> 01:06:18,886
Thank you for the tea.

568
01:07:09,978 --> 01:07:15,776
Our lightning-like assault on Arnhem
