It will be. Things couldn't be going better.
Nothing's wrong.

576
01:07:41,093 --> 01:07:44,972
Yes, I know.
That's exactly what is wrong, Harry. Yes.

577
01:07:45,597 --> 01:07:48,100
U.S. 101st AlRBORNE AREA

578
01:07:48,183 --> 01:07:50,352
THE SON BRlDGE

579
01:08:37,149 --> 01:08:39,234
Jesus Christ!

580
01:09:00,172 --> 01:09:02,257
Stay down!

581
01:09:19,733 --> 01:09:21,819
Shit!

582
01:09:24,696 --> 01:09:28,992
- There's still no contact, sir.
- Keep at it. I shall be back shortly.

583
01:09:29,076 --> 01:09:31,620
Brigadier Lathbury
can't have gone that far.

584
01:09:31,703 --> 01:09:36,124
I¡¯m sure we'll have them fixed
by the time you get back, sir.

585
01:09:41,129 --> 01:09:44,508
Can you get a message
