There's nothing, sir.
I can't contact Brigade at all, sir.

643
01:14:44,183 --> 01:14:46,310
Tried the other battalions?

644
01:14:46,393 --> 01:14:48,479
Any luck?

645
01:14:49,438 --> 01:14:52,900
- Keep trying.
- Hello, Dog Charlie Fox.

646
01:14:53,609 --> 01:14:55,569
- Order them out.
- Please, Mother.

647
01:14:55,652 --> 01:14:58,071
- This is my house.
- Perhaps by tomorrow.

648
01:14:58,197 --> 01:14:59,948
Tomorrow?

649
01:15:00,073 --> 01:15:01,950
Yes, Mother.

650
01:15:20,928 --> 01:15:24,389
Shall we have a go
at the far end now, sir?

651
01:15:24,473 --> 01:15:28,435
Having a go is hardly
textbook terminology, Harry.

652
01:15:29,353 --> 01:15:31,897
But you'll let us try, sir?

653
01:16:30,914 --> 01:16:34,501
- Down! Take cover!
- Cover fire! Quick!

654
