- Many of them?
- Can't tell, sir.

677
01:20:44,168 --> 01:20:47,337
Can only hear them at the moment.

678
01:21:49,316 --> 01:21:52,069
- Hold your fire!
- Hold your fire!

679
01:22:04,748 --> 01:22:07,251
Command. Wait for the command.

680
01:22:16,343 --> 01:22:18,846
Over there, Whitney! Look after that man!

681
01:22:19,555 --> 01:22:22,307
Open fire! Fire!

682
01:23:27,247 --> 01:23:29,333
Jesus!

683
01:24:24,012 --> 01:24:26,098
Cease firing!

684
01:24:28,016 --> 01:24:30,227
Cease firing!

685
01:24:42,156 --> 01:24:44,616
Sorry, ma'am.

686
01:24:44,700 --> 01:24:48,370
Whitney, try and rustle up
some more bandages, will you?

687
