- Forgive me, but there is a battle.

1194
02:37:53,560 --> 02:37:56,063
And we are in the process of winning it.

1195
02:37:57,230 --> 02:38:00,942
Winning and losing is not our concern.

1196
02:38:01,026 --> 02:38:03,528
Living or dying is.

1197
02:38:05,363 --> 02:38:07,741
Cease fire.

1198
02:38:07,824 --> 02:38:10,327
One hour... two.

1199
02:38:11,161 --> 02:38:14,623
Just to evacuate our wounded.

1200
